{
  "stem": "10272.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a big noise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was shaking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The whole building was shaking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He started cursing in German, God damn it, Hitler, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He-- but he's causing my-- such a-- such a tragedy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My, my family-- I don't know for my family nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They're bombing for Germany, too, and this-- and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I kept my mouth shut.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then he stopped cursing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was, was another siren calling off the, the, the alarm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got-- we stood up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he wanted to fix his-- himself to go out like-- so he gave me this gun to hold his gun, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't realize.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I didn't-- I was not even familiar how to pull, pull the trigger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was just holding it like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he trusted me the gun-- a German, German soldier trusted to the Jew the gun.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was, at the time, so emotionally-- so this is the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is the beginning of the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a German is cursing Hitler and he gives for the Jew a-- this is a signal that something is, is going on here.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I sneaked away from him without saying goodbye or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just started to run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I think he, he told me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember if, if, if I asked him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think he said something like [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fritz. ?] I was not sure-- maybe it's, it's, it's something-- I started to figure, maybe it's has something of meaning, the name.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But no, it's not the same man which, which I used to-- which I met in Budapest, encountered there in the-- but so I was going and asking people how to get to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I came to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
